《'''拆彈少年'''》（{{lang-da|'''Under sandet'''}}，{{lang-en|'''''Land of Mine'''''}}）是一部2015年[[丹麥|丹麥]]和[[德國|德國]]合拍的[[歷史片|歷史]][[劇情片|劇情片]]，由{{link-en|馬汀·贊帝維|Martin Zandvliet}}執導和編劇。電影於[[2015年多倫多國際影展|2015年多倫多國際影展]]作全球首映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/toronto-international-film-festival-announces-inaugural-platform-lineup-including-world-premiere-of-ben-wheatleys-high-rise-20150813 |title=Toronto International Film Festival Announces Inaugural Platform Lineup |accessdate=2015-08-14 |work=IndieWire |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813232137/http://www.indiewire.com/article/toronto-international-film-festival-announces-inaugural-platform-lineup-including-world-premiere-of-ben-wheatleys-high-rise-20150813 |archive-date=2015-08-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並由丹麥提交至[[第89屆奧斯卡金像獎|第89屆奧斯卡金像獎]]角逐[[奧斯卡最佳外語片獎|最佳外語片]]的電影<ref name="Denmark">{{cite web |url=http://cphpost.dk/news/war-film-submitted-as-denmarks-oscar-entry.html |title=War film submitted as Denmark’s Oscar entry |work=CPH Post |date=2016-09-19 |accessdate=2016-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919155903/http://cphpost.dk/news/war-film-submitted-as-denmarks-oscar-entry.html |archive-date=2016-09-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="HWR">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-denmarks-land-mine-picked-930779 |title=Oscars: Denmark Selects 'Land of Mine' for Foreign-Language Category |first=Scott |last=Roxborough |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2016-09-19 |accessdate=2016-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920025823/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-denmarks-land-mine-picked-930779 |archive-date=2016-09-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 劇情 ==
故事是由真實事件所啟發。敘述於1945年5月，在[[第二次世界大戰歐洲戰場的結束|納粹德國投降]]後，[[丹麥佔領時期|德佔丹麥]]被解放。一群德國少年戰俘為了負起戰爭的責任，在丹麥海邊以血肉之軀親身將眼前沙灘中所埋的數萬枚地雷全清除乾淨，才得以重回睽違多年的家園<ref>{{@movies|id=fldk43841424|title=拆彈少年 Land of Mine}}<!-- 2016-11-14 accessdate --></ref>。

== 反響 ==
《拆彈少年》贏得了影評人和觀眾的一致好評。電影在多倫多國際影展放映後，獲得了全場起立鼓掌的肯定<ref>{{cite web|last1=Monggaard|first1=Christian|title=Giant Canadian Hug|url=http://www.information.dk/545063|accessdate=2015-12-11|language=da|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222151709/http://www.information.dk/545063|archive-date=2015-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。多數影評人認為這是年度最佳的丹麥電影<ref>{{cite web|title=Review: Land of Mine|url=http://www.ekkofilm.dk/anmeldelser/under-sandet/|accessdate=2015-12-11|language=da|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151205043448/http://www.ekkofilm.dk/anmeldelser/under-sandet/|archive-date=2015-12-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Olsen|first1=Jesper|title=Review|url=http://soundvenue.com/film/2015/12/under-sandet-174023|accessdate=2015-12-11|language=da|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151204050219/http://soundvenue.com/film/2015/12/under-sandet-174023|archive-date=2015-12-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Carlsen|first1=Per Juul|title=A Kick in the Head for National Feeling|url=http://www.dr.dk/nyheder/kultur/film/anmeldelse-et-spark-i-skridtet-paa-den-danske-nationalfoelelse|accessdate=2015-12-11|language=da|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212140354/http://www.dr.dk/nyheder/kultur/film/anmeldelse-et-spark-i-skridtet-paa-den-danske-nationalfoelelse|archive-date=2015-12-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Kastrup|first1=Kim|title=Land of Mine is Number 1|url=http://ekstrabladet.dk/filmmagasinet/Filmnyheder/under-sandet-ligger-nummer-1/5863594|accessdate=2015-12-11|language=da|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222155751/http://ekstrabladet.dk/filmmagasinet/Filmnyheder/under-sandet-ligger-nummer-1/5863594|archive-date=2015-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

電影贏得了許多獎項，包括[[波迪獎|波迪獎]]的{{link-en|波迪獎最佳男主角|Bodil Award for Best Actor in a Leading Role|最佳男主角}}、{{link-en|波迪獎最佳男配角|Bodil Award for Best Actor in a Supporting Role|最佳男配角}}與{{link-en|波迪獎最佳丹麥電影|Bodil Award for Best Danish Film|最佳丹麥電影}}，[[第89届奥斯卡金像奖|第89届奥斯卡金像奖]]最佳外语片提名。

